    {
      "type": "warmup",
      "content": "<h2>Warm-up (2-3 min)</h2>\n<p>Yesterday&#39;s attitudinals:</p>\n<pre><code>happiness → ?\npity → ?\namusement → ?\n</code></pre>\n<p>(Answers: <code>.ui</code>, <code>.uu</code>, <code>.u&#39;i</code>)</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "material",
      "content": "<h2>New Material (5-7 min)</h2>\n<h3>More Attitudinals</h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Cmavo</th>\n<th>Emotion</th>\n<th>Usage</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td><code>.a&#39;o</code></td>\n<td>hope</td>\n<td><code>.a&#39;o do snada</code> (I hope you succeed)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>.au</code></td>\n<td>desire</td>\n<td><code>.au mi citka</code> (I want to eat)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>.e&#39;e</code></td>\n<td>encouragement</td>\n<td><code>.e&#39;e do troci</code> (You can do it!)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>.ie</code></td>\n<td>agreement</td>\n<td><code>.ie do drani</code> (I agree, you&#39;re right)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>.ienai</code></td>\n<td>disagreement</td>\n<td><code>.ienai ti jitfa</code> (I disagree, this is false)</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h3>Hope and Desire</h3>\n<pre><code>.a&#39;o do klama\n</code></pre>\n<p>I hope you go.</p>\n<pre><code>.au mi sipna\n</code></pre>\n<p>I want to sleep.</p>\n<h3>Agreement and Disagreement</h3>\n<pre><code>.ie\n</code></pre>\n<p>I agree. / Yes, that&#39;s right.</p>\n<pre><code>.ienai\n</code></pre>\n<p>I disagree. / No, that&#39;s wrong.</p>\n<h3>Encouragement</h3>\n<pre><code>.e&#39;e do troci\n</code></pre>\n<p>Go for it! You try!</p>\n<pre><code>.e&#39;e\n</code></pre>\n<p>You can do it!</p>\n<h3>Key Point</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p><code>.a&#39;o</code> expresses hope, <code>.au</code> desire, <code>.ie</code> agreement, <code>.e&#39;e</code> encouragement.</p>\n</blockquote>\n",
      "title": "New Material (5-7 min)"
    },
    {
      "type": "practice",
      "content": "<h2>Practice (4-5 min)</h2>\n<h3>Exercise 1: Add Emotions</h3>\n<p>Add appropriate attitudinal:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>I hope you succeed. → ?</li>\n<li>I want to eat. → ?</li>\n<li>I agree with you. → ?</li>\n</ol>\n<details>\n<summary>Answers</summary>\n\n<ol>\n<li><code>.a&#39;o do snada</code></li>\n<li><code>.au mi citka</code></li>\n<li><code>.ie</code> or <code>.ie mi tugni do</code></li>\n</ol>\n</details>\n\n<h3>Exercise 2: Respond Appropriately</h3>\n<p>Respond with attitudinal:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>&quot;This is true.&quot; — Agree → ?</li>\n<li>&quot;This is false.&quot; — Disagree → ?</li>\n<li>&quot;I will try.&quot; — Encourage → ?</li>\n</ol>\n<details>\n<summary>Answers</summary>\n\n<ol>\n<li><code>.ie</code></li>\n<li><code>.ienai</code></li>\n<li><code>.e&#39;e</code></li>\n</ol>\n</details>\n\n<h3>Exercise 3: Mixed Practice</h3>\n<p>Translate:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>I hope you are happy.</li>\n<li>I want to go.</li>\n<li>I disagree.</li>\n</ol>\n<details>\n<summary>Answers</summary>\n\n<ol>\n<li><code>.a&#39;o do gleki</code></li>\n<li><code>.au mi klama</code></li>\n<li><code>.ienai</code></li>\n</ol>\n</details>",
